\pard\f0\fs28 Fronds not more than 1 mm, floating, symmetrical, with neither roots nor veins. Bud-pouch 1, basal, median, infundibuliform, with circular opening. Raphides absent. Inflorescence consisting of 1 stamen and 1 ovary in a single cavity on the upper surface of the frond. Anthers 1-locular, dehiscing apically. Ovary globose; ovule 1, orthotropous. Fruit globose; seed smooth.
